abstract: International team is one point behind United States heading into final day of Presidents Cup golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Branden Grace delivered two big shots amid growing darkness to keep the International team a point behind the United States going into the final day of the Presidents Cup in Incheon, South Korea.
